s-bruce-campbell-will-have-meaty-role-in-spider-man-4/#more-23208|archivedate=2011-08-23|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2009年12月，有报道称[[约翰·马尔科维奇|约翰·马尔科维奇]]正在就出演反派角色“秃鹰”进行洽谈，而[[安妮·海瑟薇|安妮·海瑟薇]]则会出演费莉茜娅·哈迪一角，在原著漫画小说中，该角色的另一个秘密身份是女性超级英雄“黑猫”，但电影中的她将是一位“女秃鹰”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://movieline.com/2009/12/08/exclusive-spider-man-4-circling-john-malkovich-anne-hathaway/|title=EXCLUSIVE: Spider-Man 4 Circling John Malkovich, Anne Hathaway|publisher=Moveline.com|date=2009-12-08|accessdate=2013-05-31|last=Buchanan|first=Kyle|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/619vDNcyt?url=http://www.movieline.com/2009/12/exclusive-spider-man-4-circling-john-malkovich-anne-hathaway.php?page=all|archivedate=2011-08-23|deadurl=no}}</ref>。不过数年后雷米接受采访时表示，如果当年《蜘蛛侠4》有拍摄完成，那么安妮扮演的角色将是黑猫<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/175363-sam-raimi-confirms-that-anne-hathaway-would-have-been-his-black-cat-in-spider-man-4|title= Sam Raimi Confirms That Anne Hathaway Would Have Been His Black Cat in Spider-Man 4|publisher= SuperHeroHype.com|date= 2013-03-05|access-date= 2013-05-31|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130530030051/http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/175363-sam-raimi-confirms-that-anne-hathaway-would-have-been-his-black-cat-in-spider-man-4|archive-date= 2013-05-30|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

