2007年7月，[[漫威漫画|漫威漫画]]制片人{{link-en|阿维·阿拉德|Avi Arad}}透露了一部有关[[猛毒|猛毒]]的[[衍生作品|衍生作品]]制作计划<ref>{{cite news | first=Paul | last=Fischer | url=http://www.darkhorizons.com/news07/aviarad.php | title=Exclusive Interview: Avi Arad for "Bratz" | work=Dark Horizons | date=2007-07-24 | accessdate=2013-05-31 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071227211231/http://www.darkhorizons.com/news07/aviarad.php | archivedate=2007-12-27 | deadurl=no }}</ref>。工作室一开始委托雅各布·艾伦·埃斯戴斯（Jacob Aaron Estes）来编写剧本，但一年后因为对之不满意而没有接受。2008年9月{{link-en|保罗·沃尼克|Paul Wernick}}和略特·里斯（Rhett Reese）加入了编剧的行列<ref name=backtoback>{{cite news|first=Leslie|last=Simmons|title=Two more 'Spider-Man' films on the way|publisher=''The Hollywood Reporter'' via Reuters|date=2008-09-06|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/06/us-spiderman-idUSN0632156020080906|accessdate=2013-05-31|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/619vkvXUu?url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/06/us-spiderman-idUSN0632156020080906|archivedate=2011-08-23|deadurl=no}}</ref>，史丹·李也将在片中客串出镜<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.superherohype.com/features/articles/99039-stan-lee-to-appear-in-the-venom-spin-off|title=Stan Lee to Appear in the Venom Spin-Off|first=Edward|last=Douglas|date=2009-07-03|publisher=SuperheroHype.com|accessdate=2013-05-31|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/619w0GIZ0?url=http://www.superherohype.com/features/articles/99039-stan-lee-to-appear-in-the-venom-spin-off|archivedate=2011-08-23|deadurl=no}}</ref>。里斯之后透露他们为电影撰写了两稿剧本，工作室也正在推动其发展<ref>{{cite news|url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/09/25/venom-screenwriter-says-studio-has-script-is-pushing-forward-with-film/|title='Venom' Screenwriter Says Studio Has Script, Is 'Pushing Forward' With Film|date=2009-09-25|first=Josh|last=Wigler|publisher=MTV.com|access-date=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213120706/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/09/25/venom-screenwriter-says-studio-has-script-is-pushing-forward-with-film/|archive-date=2013-12-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年，正在改写最后一个版本《蜘蛛侠4》剧本的[[盖瑞·罗斯|盖瑞·罗斯]]获聘改写《猛毒》的剧本并亲自执导，其中将把猛毒从一开始的[[超级坏蛋|超级坏蛋]]改为一个[[反英雄|反英雄]]的形象<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming|first=Michael|title=More detail on the Ross ''Venom'' film|url=http://weblogs.variety.com/bfdealmemo/2009/10/more-details-on-the-ross-venom-film-.html|work=Variety|date=2009-10-07|accessdate=2013-05-31|archivedate=2009-10-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091011065709/http://weblogs.variety.com/bfdealmemo/2009/10/more-details-on-the-ross-venom-film-.html|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2012年3月，由于罗斯退出项目前去执导《[[饥饿游戏_(电影)|饥饿游戏]]》，于是《[[超能失控|超能失控]]》的导演[[乔什·特兰克|乔什·特兰克]]向索尼表示自己有意执导并展开了洽谈<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/chronicle-director-josh-trank-in-talks-to-helm-spider-man-spin-off-venom|title='Chronicle' Director Josh Trank In Talks To Helm 'Spider-Man' Spin-Off 'Venom'|publisher=Indiewire|date=|accessdate=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120509224734/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/chronicle-director-josh-trank-in-talks-to-helm-spider-man-spin-off-venom|archive-date=2012-05-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2012年6月，《[[超凡蜘蛛侠|超凡蜘蛛侠]]》制片人马特·托尔马奇（Matt Tolmach）接受采访时谈到搭挡制片人阿维·阿拉德的下一个项目将是一部猛毒电影，暗示该片将拥有与电影《[[复仇者联盟|复仇者联盟]]》同样的[[漫威电影宇宙|共享宇宙模式]]。“在不至于泄露任何秘密的情况下我只能说，希望这些世界终有一日能够和平共处”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.hollywood.com/news/movies/30237794/venom-movie-may-tie-into-amazing-spider-man-avengers-style-exclusive | title = 'Venom' Movie May Tie into 'Amazing Spider-Man' Avengers-Style | first = Matt | last = Patches | publisher = Hollywood.com | date = 2012-06-09 | accessdate = 2013-05-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130530060014/http://www.hollywood.com/news/movies/30237794/venom-movie-may-tie-into-amazing-spider-man-avengers-style-exclusive | archive-date = 2013-05-30 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在《超凡蜘蛛侠》中扮演弗拉什·汤普森一角的克里斯·泽尔卡表示，对汤普森一角在衍生作品中像漫威的漫画小说《{{link-en|秘密复仇者|Secret Avengers}}》中那样转变为猛毒这一设立很感兴趣<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookmovie.com/fansites/GraphicCity/news/?a=62608|title=Flash Thompson As VENOM?|publisher=ComicBookMovie.com|date=2012-06-29|access-date=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130416013840/http://www.comicbookmovie.com/fansites/GraphicCity/news/?a=62608|archive-date=2013-04-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

