====《超凡蜘蛛侠》（2012年）====
{{Main|超凡蜘蛛侠}}
《蜘蛛侠4》取消的同时，索尼也宣布这一系列将由新的导演和演员[[重启|重启]]。2012年7月3日，《超凡蜘蛛侠》以[[三维电影|三维电影]]和IMAX 3D两种立体电影格式发行上映，并重新从彼得·帕克发掘出超能力的高中时代说起<ref name="reboot">{{cite news|last=Finke|first=Nikki|last2=Fleming|first2=Mike|url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/01/urgent-spider-man-4-scrapped-as-is-raimi-and-cast-out-franchise-reboot-planned/|title='Spider-Man 4' Scrapped; Sam Rami & Tobey Maguire & Cast Out; Franchise Reboot for 2012|work=|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2010-01-11|accessdate=2013-05-31|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/619vQb9C5?url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/01/urgent-spider-man-4-scrapped-as-is-raimi-and-cast-out-franchise-reboot-planned/|archivedate=2011-08-23|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=63191|title=Spider-Man Swings Into Theaters in 3D|work=ComingSoon.net|publisher=CraveOnline|date=2010-02-10|accessdate=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019125004/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=63191|archive-date=2013-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。索尼还确认之前执导了处女作《[[和莎莫的500天|和莎莫的500天]]》的[[马克·韦布|马克·韦布]]将担任导演，{{link-en|詹姆斯·范德比尔特|James Vanderbilt}}编写剧本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/marc-webb-to-direct-new-spider-man-trilogy/|title=Marc Webb To Direct New Spider-Man Trilogy!?|publisher=/Film|last=Sciretta|first=Peter|date=2010-01-19|accessdate=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110518153418/http://www.slashfilm.com/marc-webb-to-direct-new-spider-man-trilogy/|archive-date=2011-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》称赞范德比尔特的剧本拥有坚忍不拔的现代风格，并且参考了[[克里斯多夫·诺兰|克里斯多夫·诺兰]]重启蝙蝠侠系列电影之作《[[蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻|蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻]]》的类似基调<ref>{{cite web|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2010/01/11/spider-man-reboot/|title=Next 'Spider-Man' film will be a gritty, contemporary reboot of the franchise|work=Entertainment Weekly|publisher=Time Inc.|last=Sperling|first=Nicole|date=2010-01-11|accessdate=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130705195458/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2010/01/11/spider-man-reboot/|archive-date=2013-07-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影的主要演员包括[[安德鲁·加菲尔德|安德鲁·加菲尔德]]扮演彼得·帕克<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=67468|title=It's Official! Andrew Garfield to Play Spider-Man!|work=ComingSoon.net|publisher=CraveOnline|accessdate=2013-05-31|date=2013-07-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67VoF6orY?url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=67468|archive-date=2012-05-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[艾玛·斯通|艾玛·斯通]]出演格温·斯黛茜<ref name="superherohype1">{{cite web|url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/108309-confirmed-emma-stone-to-play-gwen-stacy-in-spider-man|title=Confirmed! Emma Stone to Play Gwen Stacy in Spider-Man!|work=Superhero Hype!|publisher=CraveOnline|date=2010-10-05|accessdate=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67YfpC0GZ?url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/108309-confirmed-emma-stone-to-play-gwen-stacy-in-spider-man%7C%20title%3D%20Confirmed%21%20Emma%20Stone%20to%20Play%20Gwen%20Stacy%20in%20Spider-Man%21|archive-date=2012-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[瑞斯·伊凡斯|瑞斯·伊凡斯]]饰演大反派[[蜥蜴人|蜥蜴人]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/108677-rhys-ifans-to-play-the-spider-man-villain|title=Rhys Ifans to Play the Spider-Man Villain!|work=Superhero Hype!|publisher=CraveOnline|date=2010-10-11|accessdate=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101014034253/http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/108677-rhys-ifans-to-play-the-spider-man-villain|archive-date=2010-10-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/112063-exclusive-son-of-dr-curt-connors-cast-in-spider-man|title=Exclusive: Son of Dr. Curt Connors Cast in Spider-Man|work=Superhero Hype!|publisher=CraveOnline|date=2010-12-10|accessdate=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101215021521/http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/112063-exclusive-son-of-dr-curt-connors-cast-in-spider-man|archive-date=2010-12-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，索尼就将电影周边商品的销售权出售给了[[迪士尼公司|迪士尼公司]]的消费品部门，以换取对电影本身的全程参与权<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2012-06-27/entertainment/sns-201206270800reedbusivarietynvr1118056007-20120627_1_spider-man-franchise-andrew-garfield-peter-parker|title=Spider-Man campaign aims to ensnare femmes: Sony enlists 400 promo partners as it looks to grow fanbase for webslinging franchise|date=2012-06-27|accessdate=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130606123437/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2012-06-27/entertainment/sns-201206270800reedbusivarietynvr1118056007-20120627_1_spider-man-franchise-andrew-garfield-peter-parker|archive-date=2013-06-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

