ref>。2011年8月，索尼宣布续集还在2014年5月2日发行，然而前作《超凡蜘蛛侠》也要再过近一年才会上映<ref>{{cite news | first=Nikki | last=Finke | url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/08/sony-dates-amazing-spider-man-sequel/ | title=Sony Dates 'Amazing Spider-Man' Sequel | accessdate=2013-05-31 | publisher=Deadline.com | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/619p0SzmS?url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/08/sony-dates-amazing-spider-man-sequel/ | archivedate=2011-08-23 | deadurl=no }}</ref>。安德鲁·加菲尔德在《超凡蜘蛛侠》发行前几天表示，“如果我们拍（续集）的话，我希望我能演吧——我希望他们让我演……他们都已经宣布上映日期啦，但现在都还没个剧本呢！所以我们现在都只能先干点别的。”<ref name=thr-hopes>{{cite news | title = Andrew Garfield Hopes to Star in 'Spider-Man' Sequel | date = 2012-06-27 | first = Erin | last = Carlson | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/andrew-garfield-hopes-star-spider-342498 | work = The Hollywood Reporter | accessdate = 2013-05-31 | archivedate = 2012-06-27 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/68jxlOVRb?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/andrew-garfield-hopes-star-spider-342498 | deadurl = no }}</ref>2012年9月14日，加菲尔德和马克·韦布都确认将回归续集继续担任主演和导演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/09/28/andrew-garfield-marc-webb-amazing-spider-man-2_n_1924327.html?utm_hp_ref=entertainment |title=Andrew Garfield & Marc Webb Return For 'Amazing Spider-Man 2' |work=Huffington Post |date=2012-09-28 |accessdate=2013-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213155445/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/09/28/andrew-garfield-marc-webb-amazing-spider-man-2_n_1924327.html?utm_hp_ref=entertainment |archive-date=2013-12-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/amazing-spider-man-sequel-returns-375025 |title=Andrew Garfield and Director Marc Webb to Return for 'Amazing Spider-Man' Sequel |last=Siegel |first=Tatiana |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2012-09-28 |accessdate=2013-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121031134403/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/amazing-spider-man-sequel-returns-375025 |archive-date=2012-10-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同时下一部续集也已在计划之中<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/171483-amazing-spider-man-planned-as-trilogy | title = The Amazing Spider-Man Planned as Trilogy | publisher = SuperHeroHype | date = 2012-07-05 | access-date = 2013-05-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130609021545/http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/171483-amazing-spider-man-planned-as-trilogy | archive-date = 2013-06-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。曾出演《蜘蛛侠》三部曲的[[J·K·西蒙斯|J·K·西蒙斯]]表示希望可以在新的系列中继续出演{{lang|en|J}}·乔纳·詹姆森<ref>{{cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/amazing-spiderman-2-j-jonah-jameson-jk-simmons |title='Amazing Spider-Man 2′: Should J.K. Simmons Return as J. Jonah Jameson? |publisher=Screenrant |last=Outlaw |first=Kofi |date=2012-08-06 |accessdate=2013-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130424233729/http://screenrant.com/amazing-spiderman-2-j-jonah-jameson-jk-simmons/ |archive-date=2013-04-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年10月10日，电影公司宣布请谢琳·伍德蕾在首部续集中出演玛丽·简·沃森，这一说法之后得到进一步证实，伍德蕾将在两部续集中出演这一角色，但在首部续集中只是个小配角，第二部续集中则是主演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eonline.com/news/353151/shailene-woodley-in-talks-for-amazing-spider-man-sequel?cmpid=rss-000000-rssfeed-365-topstories&utm_source=eonline&utm_medium=rssfeeds&utm_campaign=rss_topstories |title=Shailene Woodley In Talks For Amazing Spider Man Sequel |publisher=E! Online |accessdate=2013-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204225623/http://www.eonline.com/news/353151/shailene-woodley-in-talks-for-amazing-spider-man-sequel?cmpid=rss-000000-rssfeed-365-topstories&utm_source=eonline&utm_medium=rssfeeds&utm_campaign=rss_topstories |archive-date=2013-12-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/shailene-woodley-talks-spider-man-377915 |title=Shailene Woodley in Talks for 'Spider-Man 2' |publisher=Hollywood Reporter |date=2011-11-17 |accessdate=2013-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121011184844/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/shailene-woodley-talks-spider-man-377915 |archive-date=2012-10-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年11月1日，公司宣布[[杰米·福克斯|杰米·福克斯]]将加盟《超凡蜘蛛侠2》出演反派“电光人”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2012/film/news/jamie-foxx-in-talks-to-play-spider-man-2-villain-1118061562/ |title=Jamie Foxx in early talks to play 'Spider-Man 2' villain |publisher=Variety |date=2012-11-01 |accessdate=2013-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530092234/http://variety.com/2012/film/news/jamie-foxx-in-talks-to-play-spider-man-2-villain-1118061562/ |archive-date=2013-05-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之后这一消息也得到了确认<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1699031/amazing-spider-man-2-villian-electro.jhtml |title=Exclusive: 'Spider-Man' Villain Jamie Foxx Reveals Major Origin Details |publisher=MTV |date=2012-12-17 |access-date=2013-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204052618/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1699031/amazing-spider-man-2-villian-electro.jhtml |archive-date=2013-12-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年11月16日有消息称哈里·奥斯本一角将出现在续集中，2012年12月3日，马克·韦布透露戴恩·德哈恩将出演该角色<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/MarcW/status/275681673650253824 |title=Meet Harry Osborn. @danedehaan |publisher=Twitter |date=2012-12-03 |accessdate=2013-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130815075213/https://twitter.com/MarcW/status/275681673650253824 |archive-date=2013-08-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年2月，公司宣布保罗·吉亚玛提将出演另一位反面角色亚历克斯·塞斯维奇（犀牛）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookmovie.com/fansites/JoshWildingNewsAndReviews/news/?a=73840|title=THE AMAZING SPIDER-MAN 2 Title and Synopsis Revealed; Colm Feore And Paul Giamatti Join Cast|work=ComicBookMovie.com|date=2013-02-05|accessdate=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130531210517/http://www.comicbookmovie.com/fansites/JoshWildingNewsAndReviews/news/?a=73840|archive-date=2013-05-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，而[[克里斯·库珀|克里斯·库珀]]则会出演诺曼·奥斯本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/amazing-spider-man-chris-cooper-424874|title='Amazing Spider-Man 2': Chris Cooper to Play Green Goblin|last=Siegel|first=Tatiana|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2013-02-27|accessdate=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130301012051/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/amazing-spider-man-chris-cooper-424874|archive-date=2013-03-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====未製作====
2014年《[[蜘蛛人驚奇再起2：電光之戰|蜘蛛人驚奇再起2：電光之戰]]》片尾預告續集出現新敵人將組合[[邪惡六人組|邪惡六人組]]，另外索尼表示將可能推出[[邪惡六人組|邪惡六人組]]及[[猛毒|猛毒]]的外傳電影。<ref>[http://www.nownews.com/n/2014/04/22/1202696 邪惡六人組搶先曝光 《蜘蛛人3》未演先轟動] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nownews.com/n/2014/04/22/1202696 |date=20170603114309 }},NOWnews 2014.04.22 翁新涵</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hypesphere.com/?p=24027 |title=索尼影業確定拍攝「蜘蛛人系列」獨立電影「猛毒」以及「邪惡六人組」 |access-date=2017-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181008174958/https://www.hypesphere.com/?p=24027 |archive-date=2018-10-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>但隨著該系列電影再次重啟之後，相關電影計劃都已經停擺。
===潛在項目===
2016年Sony與[[漫威影業|漫威影業]]合作的蜘蛛人系列電影外，Sony還有意創作獨立電影《[[猛毒|猛毒]]》《[[黑貓_(漫威)|黑貓]]》《[[銀貂|銀貂]]》<ref>[https://www.forbes.com/sites/markhughes/2017/03/28/confirmed-spider-man-remains-in-mcu-for-at-least-3-more-films/#7394066a1230 Confirmed: Spider-Man Remains In MCU For At Least 3 More Films] {{Wayback|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/markhughes/2017/03/28/confirmed-spider-man-remains-in-mcu-for-at-least-3-more-films/#7394066a1230 |date=20170329034315 }},2017.3.28 Forbes</ref>。2018年，《[[猛毒_(電影)|猛毒]]》上映。

==回歸漫威電影宇宙的许可协议==

2014年12月，有报道称索尼与漫威正讨论允许将蜘蛛侠进入[[漫威电影宇宙|漫威电影宇宙]]的电影《美国队长3》中，而蜘蛛侠系列电影版权将依然属于索尼。据说这些计划曾被提出。相反，索尼曾考虑让萨姆·莱米回归执导新三部曲，以及和[[菲尔·洛德和克里斯托弗·米勒|菲尔·洛德和克里斯托弗·米勒]]的一部动画喜剧。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/12/09/sony-marvel-discussed-spider-man-movie-crossover/|title=Sony, Marvel Discussed Spider-Man Movie Crossover|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=2014-12-09|access-date=2015-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210035701/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/12/09/sony-marvel-discussed-spider-man-movie-crossover/|archive-date=2014-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/spider-man-animated-comedy-marvel-crossover/|title=Sony Leak Reveals Studio Considering Lord/Miller Spider-Man Comedy, Marvel Crossover|last=Han|first=Angie|work=FilmSlash|date=2014-12-09|access-date=2015-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170618135112/http://www.slashfilm.com/spider-man-animated-comedy-marvel-crossover/|archive-date=2017-06-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>而在2015年2月9日，索尼影视与[[漫威影业|漫威影业]]却宣布，蜘蛛侠将会出现在漫威电影宇宙中，并将在2017年6月28日发布一部独立影片，由漫威影业主席[[凯文·菲戈|凯文·菲戈]]和{{le|艾米·帕斯卡|Amy Pascal}}共同制作。索尼影视将依然拥有蜘蛛侠系列电影的的财务权、发行权以及最终创作权。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://marvel.com/news/movies/24062/sony_pictures_entertainment_brings_marvel_studios_into_the_amazing_world_of_spider-man|title=Sony Pictures Entertainment Brings Marvel Studios Into The Amazing World Of Spider-Man|publisher=[[Marvel_Comics|Marvel.com]]|date=2015-02-09|accessdate=2015-02-10|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6WEIuzniG?url=http://marvel.com/news/movies/24062/sony_pictures_entertainment_brings_marvel_studios_into_the_amazing_world_of_spider-man|archivedate=2015-02-10|deadurl=no}}</ref>《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》报道称，蜘蛛侠将出现于2016年影片《[[美国队长3|美国队长3]]》中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/marvel-and-sony-reach-deal-on-spider-man-movie-production-1423546677|title=Marvel and Sony Reach Deal on Spider-Man Movie Production|author=Ben Fritz|date=2015-02-10|work=WSJ|accessdate=2015-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402231302/http://www.wsj.com/articles/marvel-and-sony-reach-deal-on-spider-man-movie-production-1423546677|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年6月23日，漫威和索尼官方确认[[汤姆·赫兰德|汤姆·赫兰德]]将饰演蜘蛛侠，而[[乔恩·沃茨|乔恩·沃茨]]将执导该新版蜘蛛侠电影。赫兰德还将以一名配角的身份出现在《[[美國隊長3：英雄內戰|美國隊長3：英雄內戰]]》中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://marvel.com/news/movies/24758/sony_pictures_and_marvel_studios_find_their_spider-man_star_and_director|title=Sony Pictures and Marvel Studios Find Their 'Spider-Man' Star and Director|publisher=Marvel|date=2015-06-23|accessdate=2016-05-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ZWEoSWCY?url=http://marvel.com/news/movies/24758/sony_pictures_and_marvel_studios_find_their_spider-man_star_and_director|archive-date=2015-06-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/tom-holland-spider-man-new-movie-1201510563/|title=Tom Holland Is the new Spider-Man, Jon Watts to Direct Film|publisher=Variety|last=Kroll|first=Justin|date=2015-06-23|accessdate=2016-05-06}}</ref>。

===《美國隊長3：英雄內戰》（2016年）===
{{Main|美國隊長3：英雄內戰}}
報導指根據許可協議，蜘蛛俠將會於2016年上映的《美國隊長3：英雄內戰》中出現在漫威電影宇宙<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/marvel-and-sony-reach-deal-on-spider-man-movie-production-1423546677|title=Marvel and Sony Reach Deal on Spider-Man Movie Production|author=Ben Fritz|date=2015-02-10|work=The Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2016-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402231302/http://www.wsj.com/articles/marvel-and-sony-reach-deal-on-spider-man-movie-production-1423546677|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Spider-Man-Civil-War">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/russo-brothers-sign-first-look-deal-with-sony-1201445430/|title=Russo Brothers Sign First-Look Deal with Sony|last=McNary|first=David|publisher=Variety.com|date=2015-03-03|accessdate=2016-05-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6WlIW7oaA?url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/russo-brothers-sign-first-look-deal-with-sony-1201445430/|archivedate=2015-03-03|deadurl=no}}</ref>。《美國隊長3：英雄內戰》的導演[[羅素兄弟|安東尼·羅素和喬·羅素]]為了讓蜘蛛俠得以出現在電影裏，花了幾個月作遊說工作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/captain-america-civil-war-avengers-3-infinity-war-updates-russo-brothers/|title=‘Captain America: Civil War’ Directors on Landing Spider-Man, ‘Infinity War’ Shooting Schedule|last=Cabin|first=Chris|publisher=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|date=2016-01-14|accessdate=2016-01-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108133217/https://collider.com/captain-america-civil-war-avengers-3-infinity-war-updates-russo-brothers/|archivedate=2020-11-08|deadurl=no}}</ref>。安東尼·羅素指，雖然漫威跟他們說要準備協議失敗後的備用計劃，但他們從未為此準備，因為將蜘蛛俠帶進這部電影對他們來說十分重要，並指「我們只設想了有蜘蛛俠的電影版本」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/article/anthony-russo-reveals-spider-man-was-always-plan-a-for-captain-america-civil-war|title=Anthony Russo Reveals Spider-Man Was Always "Plan A" For "Captain America: Civil War"|last=Damore|first=Meagan|publisher={{link-en|Comic Book Resources|Comic Book Resources}}|date=2015-12-07|accessdate=2015-12-08|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dcGdQYIa?url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/article/anthony-russo-reveals-spider-man-was-always-plan-a-for-captain-america-civil-war|archivedate=2015-12-08|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2015年5月尾，[[阿薩·巴特菲爾德|阿薩·巴特菲爾德]]、[[湯姆·霍蘭|湯姆·霍蘭]]、{{link-en|猶大·路易斯|Judah Lewis}}、{{link-en|馬修·林茲|Matthew Lintz}}、{{link-en|查理·普魯瑪|Charlie Plummer}}和[[查理·羅|查理·羅]]為蜘蛛俠一角試鏡，在電影中跟蜘蛛俠一角有對手戲、飾演[[鐵甲奇俠|鐵甲奇俠]]的[[小勞勃·道尼|小勞勃·道尼]]也有參與評審過程<ref name="SpideyCastingCall">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/spider-man-hopefuls-screen-test-798995|title=Spider-Man Hopefuls Screen-Test in Atlanta as Marvel Decision Nears (Exclusive)|last=Kit|first=Borys|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2015-05-30|accessdate=2015-05-30|archivedate=2015-06-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150623143635/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/spider-man-hopefuls-screen-test-798995|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="THRCastingSecrets">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/how-new-spider-man-team-804569|title=Robert Downey Jr. and Secret Screen-Tests: How the New 'Spider-Man' Team Was Chosen|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|last2=Siegel|first2=Tatiana|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2015-06-23|accessdate=2015-06-25|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ZXachmg2?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/how-new-spider-man-team-804569|archivedate=2015-06-25|deadurl=no}}</ref>。他們六人從1,500名演員中脫穎而出，須在菲戈、帕斯卡和羅素兄弟面前試演<ref name="SpideyCastingCall" />。6月，菲戈和帕斯卡將人選收窄至荷蘭和羅兩人。兩人再次跟道尼試演，其中荷蘭再跟飾演[[美國隊長|美國隊長]]的[[基斯·伊雲斯|基斯·伊雲斯]]試演<ref name="THRCastingSecrets" />。2015年6月23日，索尼和漫威聯合公布荷蘭將飾演蜘蛛俠一角<ref name=MarvelSonyJune23>{{cite press release| url=http://marvel.com/news/movies/24758/sony_pictures_and_marvel_studios_find_their_spider-man_star_and_director| title=Sony Pictures and Marvel Studios Find Their 'Spider-Man' Star and Director| date=2015-06-23| accessdate=2015-06-24| publisher=Marvel.com| archivedate=2015-06-24| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ZWEoSWCY?url=http://marvel.com/news/movies/24758/sony_pictures_and_marvel_studios_find_their_spider-man_star_and_director| deadurl=no}}</ref>。

