ider-man_homecoming_introduces_its_villain|archivedate=2016-07-24|deadurl=no}}</ref>。霍蘭德、托梅和唐尼分別飾演彼得·帕克 / 蜘蛛人、梅·帕克與東尼·史塔克 / 鋼鐵人的角色<ref name="DowneySMH">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/robert-downey-jr-joins-spider-885829 |title=Robert Downey Jr. Joins 'Spider-Man: Homecoming' |last=Kit |first=Borys |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2016-04-21 |accessdate=2016-04-21 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6gwJpLINa?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/robert-downey-jr-joins-spider-885829 |archivedate=2016-04-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，[[麥可·基頓|麥可·基頓]]將於電影中詮釋[[禿鷹_(漫威漫畫)|亞德里安·圖姆斯 / 禿鷹]]<ref name="SDCC2016" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/12/08/exclusive-sneak-peek-spider-man-homecoming-first-look-new-photo/95058230/ |title=Exclusive photo: Spider-Man Tom Holland unmasked in 'Homecoming' |last=Truitt |first=Brian |work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |date=2016-12-08 |accessdate=2016-12-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221010824/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/12/08/exclusive-sneak-peek-spider-man-homecoming-first-look-new-photo/95058230/?hootPostID=c358745e046dd8ff38fd40a756a92130 |archivedate=2016-12-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。製作始於喬治亞州的亞特蘭大，10月結束<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/06/20/chris-pratt-tom-holland-james-gunn-spider-man-homecoming |title=Chris Pratt, Tom Holland cross paths as Spider-Man: Homecoming starts filming |last=Coggan |first=Devan |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2016-06-20 |accessdate=2016-06-20 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6iQA0y96p?url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/06/20/chris-pratt-tom-holland-james-gunn-spider-man-homecoming |archivedate=2016-06-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.11alive.com/news/captain-america-civil-war-shot-in-around-atlanta/170019060 |title="Captain America: Civil War" was shot in, around Atlanta |last=Leslie |first=Jennifer |publisher={{link-en|WXIA-TV|WXIA-TV}} |date=2016-05-05 |accessdate=2016-05-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6hHGU1Due?url=http://www.11alive.com/news/captain-america-civil-war-shot-in-around-atlanta/170019060 |archivedate=2016-05-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="FilmingWrap">{{cite web |url=http://comicbook.com/marvel/2016/10/02/tom-holland-shares-photo-from-spider-man-homecomings-last-day-of/ |title=Tom Holland Shares Photo From Spider-Man: Homecoming's Last Day Of Filming |last=Peters |first=Megan |publisher=Comicbook.com |date=2016-10-02 |accessdate=2016-10-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6kyNCNvSz?url=http://comicbook.com/marvel/2016/10/02/tom-holland-shares-photo-from-spider-man-homecomings-last-day-of/ |archivedate=2016-10-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

