==迴响==

===奥斯卡金像奖===
《蜘蛛侠》获得了[[第75届奥斯卡金像奖|第75届奥斯卡金像奖]][[奥斯卡最佳视觉效果奖|视觉效果]]、音效两项提名，但最终都没有获奖<ref name="Oscars2003">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/75th-winners.html |title=The 75th Academy Awards (2003) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=2013-05-31 |work=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224032945/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/75th-winners.html |archive-date=2013-12-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；《蜘蛛侠2》获得了[[第77届奥斯卡金像奖|第77届奥斯卡金像奖]]视觉效果、音效、[[奥斯卡最佳音效剪辑奖|音效剪辑]]3项提名，最终拿下了视觉效果奖<ref name="Oscars2005">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/77th-winners.html |title=The 77th Academy Awards (2005) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=2013-05-30 |work=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610213020/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/77th-winners.html |archivedate=2014-06-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

===票房表现===
《蜘蛛侠》三部曲每一部首映当天都会创下一个新的票房纪录<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/briefing/spiderman.htm | title=Spider-Man Special Briefing | work=Box Office Mojo | accessdate=2013-05-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130516015622/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/briefing/spiderman.htm | archive-date=2013-05-16 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。这三部曲都是惊奇漫画改编的电影中美国票房最高的5部之一，其中《蜘蛛侠》列第二位，《蜘蛛侠2》第四，《蜘蛛侠3》第五<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=marvelcomics.htm | title=Marvel Comics Movies | work=Box Office Mojo | accessdate=2013-05-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302025723/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=marvelcomics.htm | archive-date=2016-03-02 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。这三部曲还是美国历史上所有[[超级英雄|超级英雄]]电影中票房最高的十部电影之一，《蜘蛛侠》第四位，《蜘蛛侠2》第六位，《蜘蛛侠3》第七位<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=superhero.htm | title=Superhero Movies | work=Box Office Mojo | accessdate=2013-05-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130710062646/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=superhero.htm | archive-date=2013-07-10 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，蜘蛛侠三部曲还是索尼/哥伦比亚电影公司票房最高的三部电影<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/studio/chart/?studio=sony.htm | title=Sony / Columbia All Time Box Office Results | work=Box Office Mojo | accessdate=2013-05-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510004627/http://boxofficemojo.com/studio/chart/?studio=sony.htm | archive-date=2013-05-10 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

